{
  "stem": "766.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, yes, I married two months before the war and my husband is in the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Where he is, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, if you tell us-- if you don't have an a diamond, who has diamonds?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should report.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we will tell you where your husband is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So at that time, the one said-- and I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, how can he know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He doesn't even know the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I only looked at him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one said to the other, look at that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She looks at you, and she had a fresh look-- and fresh and bleak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At least I showed him I had a freshened look, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because-- That was the only defense you had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He tells me-- he will tell me and I are going to report I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wouldn't report.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he wanted to trick me in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was called at the same time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he heard from outside, they beat-- they always to the emergency room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought people from the KRIPO.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we called it [NON-ENGLISH] because it was inflammation of those hard-- like a board and red and bleeding because they beat up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when my brother told me-- because it wasn't with me-- that when they interrogated him and he also said he doesn't know, he said if you don't talk, you-- it will be with you what you hear over there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Over there is your [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This they knew to say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The angel of death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't beat him either up, and not me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
